    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <actionDate>2017-01-12</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>The bill changes the days on which the POW/MIA flag is required to be displayed at specified locations to all days on which the U.S. flag is displayed. (Current law requires the POW/MIA flag to be displayed only on Armed Forces Day, Memorial Day, Flag Day, Independence Day, National POW/MIA Recognition Day, and Veterans Day.)</p>]]></text>
